Invocation Name: chris fantastic powell
des: Listen to the latest lectures and speaker series from Chris Fantastic Powell. No one is born a failure nor born a success you have to choose. Which team do you use to win or lose in your life, business, or relationship. There are two teams The Oh No's and The Lets Go's. Are you ready to know more. When listening you can say "Alexa, next" to play the next series or "Alexa, previous".
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
